                    "body": "Thanks!\n\nThe implementation is here: https://github.com/pcmoritz/arrow/tree/rowbatchsize\n\nI'd like to write a test, is there any way to see how many bytes have been written to the MemorySource? And is it enough to create a PR in git to contribute the code back?\n",
